{"tid":1783991,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"看抗爭的危機與轉機","createTime":"2019-12-15T10:13:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-15T10:50:55.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e2e9e36bad5fd8cf8f4ef7870abd81039a1a54e4","tid":1783991,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T10:13:43.000Z","msg":"下文將分別以「藍絲」和「黃絲」指稱「傾向支持建制派的市民」及「傾向支持示威者的市民」<br />\n以上分析資料分別取自連登討論區（LIHKG，簡稱連登）及香港討論區（<a href=\"http://Discuss.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FDiscuss.com.hk&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWuzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=bf03e8c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Discuss.com.hk</a>，簡稱香討）<br />\n<br />\n前者使用者主要為黃絲（相對上傾向泛民），後者使用者主要為藍絲（相對上傾向建制，亦有相對中立及淺黃）<br />\n<br />\n從而分析雙方陣營的觀點及立場的轉變以方便討論<br />\n<br />\n根據之前的數據分析，局勢一如預計之中漸轉平靜，加上鄧炳強上任之後一改警隊處事作風，在媒體前面未有作大規模搜捕，轉而在集會之後上門搜捕前線示威者，避免再次出現各種大型衝突的場面，再加上政府避免犯錯，沒有再出來刺激市民，這都無疑令到整個抗爭熱度慢慢地緩和下來。<br />\n<br />\n的而且確，單純看大家的關注度，整個抗爭出現了前所未有的大危機，實在令人擔心，可是，我們是不是能夠從這些數據當中找出一些別人看不到的東西，從而找出轉機呢？<br />\n<br />\n這次筆者會抽取比較多的數據來比較分析，希望可以帶來新的想法給各位讀者。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/01_UZjOU_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F01_UZjOU_1200x0.jpg&h=00758ffb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n數據重點：黃絲士氣尚可維持，可是已經連續一個月下降，而關注度更是跌至這次抗爭發生以來的最低點。<br />\n<br />\n根據圖 1.1 的顯示，黃絲的 Momentum 已經持續一個月下跌，雖然未跌至抗爭最低點（現為 2.45），對於政府慢慢的學聰明了之外，緊接著亦是聖誕佳節，如果抗爭之路沒辦法找到新出路或是突破點，跌勢將會繼續無法止住。 此外，黃絲的關注度情況更讓人擔心，跟 Momentum 一樣連續下降之餘，關注度更是跌到抗爭發生後的最低點（現為 45%），同一時間值得我們注意的是，藍絲的關注度有所回升，如果這個情況一直維持，就會出現 2014 雨傘時候的狀況，出現黃金交叉，最後運動結束。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/02_pN9Bi_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F02_pN9Bi_1200x0.jpg&h=dffb90c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據圖 1.2 的顯示，我們可以看到上星期日，從 heatmap 中顯示遊行的數值去到 20.62%，前後數天也停留在 13-17% 左右，可以看得出大家還是關注的，只是星期天一過了，數值就大跌，這裡我們可以觀察到現在不像抗爭初期，能夠一直保持著關注與熱度，但香港人還是沒有放棄，遇上大事還是會走出來表達。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/03_eBXcT_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F03_eBXcT_1200x0.jpg&h=0cad7991&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據圖 1.3 的顯示，上星期的遊行在藍絲間也引起關注（9.58 及 12.05%），另外值得一提的是，移民的數值也有 2% 左右。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/04_XR4zm_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F04_XR4zm_1200x0.jpg&h=2e70c751&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據圖 1.4 的顯示，由於開審了上環暴動案關係，我們可以看到撤回暴動的討論突然上升了。<br />\n<br />\n總結：局勢表面平靜，政府清算未停。<br />\n<br />\n士氣跟關注度下降，是不能否定的事實。<br />\n<br />\n可是同樣地，政府的清算行動依然沒有一絲停下來的意思，他們可以喪心命狂到連周同學的出殯也不放過，如果香港人在這一個時間放棄，那麼往後就只會有更多的周同學出現。<br />\n<br />\n我們必須要整理好心情，重新裝備自己再出發，努力為這場抗爭找出轉機。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%A4%A7%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E7%9C%8B%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%B1%E6%A9%9F%E8%88%87%E8%BD%89%E6%A9%9F/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2595%25B8%25E6%2593%259A%25E7%259C%258B%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%258D%25B1%25E6%25A9%259F%25E8%2588%2587%25E8%25BD%2589%25E6%25A9%259F%2F&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWuzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=8972da6c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2595%25B8%25E6%2593%259A%25E7%259C%258B%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%258D%25B1%25E6%25A9%259F%25E8%2588%2587%25E8%25BD%2589%25E6%25A9%259F%2F&h=05a1fbeb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%A4%A7%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E7%9C%8B%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%B1%E6%A9%9F%E8%88%87%E8%BD%89%E6%A9%9F/</a>"},{"pid":"584e9332cc4d3570652e07968e957a446ff6b1f1","tid":1783991,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T10:14:16.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[你今日FC咗未] 全港最大的Fact Check平台已經推出了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776631\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776631</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f776ef461e6db276fe130033ed5d29160c02d93d","tid":1783991,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"584e9332cc4d3570652e07968e957a446ff6b1f1","tid":1783991,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T10:14:16.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[你今日FC咗未] 全港最大的Fact Check平台已經推出了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776631\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776631</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T10:14:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37258ecd8d750d22841f0e17affbc5156d6af3c2","tid":1783991,"uid":202524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T10:41:02.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借個位黎<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">德國戰線要人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ebcda9e7c1c3162996915fc8706ebaaf4ea60ea7","tid":1783991,"uid":34514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T10:44:00.000Z","msg":"依家要多啲文宣呀! 有低門檻玩法, 入嚟睇吓啦!<br />\n[行動] 解決目前文宣困局--A4 size label 周圍貼! 人人都係文宣組!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1783119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1783119</a>"},{"pid":"11e8c833fca4fc8eb456d0e18941f5f6a6e60f03","tid":1783991,"uid":37722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T10:45:15.000Z","msg":"的確feel到士氣下跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n主要原因我相信係因為行動力高既人數愈黎愈少"},{"pid":"112e48afcc227043142e46e67ce6790da6a06bb1","tid":1783991,"uid":1072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T10:50:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"180c204736cfef234b78d0a74505483211f745d6","tid":1783991,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T10:50:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}